</p></entry><entry colname="col2" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">8 x 0.7L UV gel ink bottles (C, M, Y, K and optional W) 
</p></entry><entry colname="col3" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><fig id="GUID-24B6F6EE-CAD2-4CB3-A605-5D5877F64059" class="- topic/fig "><image href="GUID-FD913673-B5E3-45FF-8EC5-1D47ACA0345A-low.png" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-FD913673-B5E3-45FF-8EC5-1D47ACA0345A-low.png"/></fig></entry></row><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">6 
