</p></entry><entry colname="col2" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p "> A roll of media: 
</p><ul class="- topic/ul "><li class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p ">minimum width &gt;= 50 inch (1520 mm) 
</p></li><li class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p "> white and smooth surface 
</p></li><li class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p "> the media should not be too thin 
</p></li><li class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p "> the media should also be usable in loose winding 
</p></li><li class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p "> the media should fall in one of the media categories "film", "paper", "vinyl". 
</p></li></ul><p class="- topic/p ">Example: MPI 2000 (preferred). 
</p><note id="GUID-96AF4CD8-37DE-40A5-9334-B8E4D20A1052" class="- topic/note "><p class="- topic/p "> Required to do the calibrations during the installation. 
</p></note></entry><entry colname="col3" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><fig id="GUID-0D52981F-DDB9-43A3-A299-7714F1B74FC1" class="- topic/fig "><image href="GUID-E6F2692F-C8B6-4394-A0B9-A226898C85F1-low.png" keyref="" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-E6F2692F-C8B6-4394-A0B9-A226898C85F1-low.png"/></fig></entry></row><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">8 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Optional: 2 x Frame Filters. In case of an exhaust option it is not needed. 
</p><p class="- topic/p ">or 
</p><p class="- topic/p ">Optional: Exhaust tube. 
</p><note id="GUID-1C00C874-5793-445D-8728-29E1768077E8" class="- topic/note "><p class="- topic/p ">Exhaust tube needs to be ordered on the order form. 
</p></note></entry><entry colname="col3" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><fig id="GUID-32F57088-CC45-459E-A258-56B0DB2F7D60" class="- topic/fig "><image href="GUID-B3F1B171-6337-49AD-81C8-EBD75957E2EE-low.png" keyref="" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-B3F1B171-6337-49AD-81C8-EBD75957E2EE-low.png"/></fig></entry></row></tbody></tgroup></table></section></conbody><related-links class="- topic/related-links "><linkpool class="- topic/linkpool " mapkeyref="GUID-8A41CFEA-5928-4042-A2CB-507A5D034160"><link class="- topic/link " mapclass="- map/topicref " format="dita" type="concept" href="generated-topic-GUID-7D3F358C-1AB9-4A5D-9B0E-C75D689F152E.xml" role="parent"><?ditaot usertext?><linktext class="- topic/linktext "><?ditaot usertext?>Installation</linktext></link></linkpool></related-links>
